Parliament, Monday, 9 September 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Basic Education will tomorrow have a joint meeting with the Portfolio Committee on Police and the Portfolio Committee on Social Development to receive a briefing on safety and security in schools (including educators and learners) by the Department of Basic Education, the South African Police Service and the Department of Social Development. Details are as follows: 
	Date: Tuesday, 10 September 2019
	Time: 09:30
	Venue: Committee Room 1, Upper Ground Floor, 90 Plein Street Building. ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
	Tel: 021 403 8437
	Cell: 081 703 9542
